channel.title: DeltaScape version of RuneKeep
channel.description:
hi im gonna make a server thats a deltascape source version of runekeep. i need 2-4 hosters, a coder, a command generator, and some test hosters. this server will also have a .tk website with forums and a webclient. Reasons for WebClient: #1. The source is DeltaScape #2. Bluurs client is a deltascape client
Reasons for DeltaScape Source: #1. You have to work for your skills and items #2. Syi Proof (no crashes) #3. very stable, can hold up to 200 players
so email me at Skype_ftw@yahoo.ca and we can talk
-FatalBluur

Thank you
-FatalBluur
